<body>
<h1 align="center">This should be white and centered.</h1>

<h1 align="center" style="border:1px; border-style:solid; background-color:blue; border-color:red; padding: .2em;" > Border is 1px. Border is solid. Padding is .2 . Centered. </h1>
<h1 align="center" style="border:2px; border-style:double; background-color:green;border-color:red; padding: .1em;" > Border is 2px. Border is double. Padding is .1 . Centered. </h1>
<h1 align="left" style="border:5px; border-style:dotted; background-color:yellow; border-color:red; padding: .5em;" > Border is 5px. Border is dotted. Padding is .5 . Left. </h1>
<h1 align="right" style="border:10px; border-style:dashed; border-color:red; padding: 1em;" > Border is 10px. Border is dashed. Padding is 1 . Right. </h1>
<h1 align="center" style="border:15px; border-style:double; border-color:red; padding: 3em;" > Border is 15px. Border is double. Padding is 3 . Centered. </h1>
<h1 aligh="left" style="border:20px; border-style:groove; border-color:red; padding: 5em;" > Border is 20px. Border is groove. Padding is 5 . Left. </h1>
<h1 align="center" style="border:25px; border-style:ridge; background-color:white; color:black; border-color:red; padding: 1em;" > Border is 25px. Border is ridge. Padding is 1 . Centered. </h1>
<p align="center">This assigns attributs in head style.</p>


